title: Match of the Day 22nd March 2008 XviD
description:
Sat 22 Mar, 10:25 pm - 11:45 pm 80mins

Gary Lineker presents highlights of Premier League matches, with expert analysis from Alan Hansen and Mark Lawrenson. With the leading pack playing on Sunday, attention turns to the fight for survival at the other end of the table. 

Sunderland and Wigan face tough away matches at Aston Villa and Blackburn respectively, while there are crucial home games for Bolton against Manchester City and for Reading against Birmingham City. In addition, Kevin Keegan&#039;s Newcastle host Fulham, who picked up an extremely rare away victory at St James&#039; Park last season.


MOTD running order

Newcastle v Fulham
Aston Villa v Sunderland
Blackburn v Wigan
Reading v Birmingham
Everton v West Ham
Tottenham v Portsmouth
Bolton v Man City
Middlesbrough v Derby
